Things to manage using puppet
=============================

- postfix
- dovecot
- locales
- root's .bashrc (DEBIAN_FRONTEND, unset HISTFILE)
- mariadb
- spamassassin
- do profiles and roles
- docker, service and either of this containers running:
  - https://github.com/containrrr/watchtower
  - https://github.com/pyouroboros/ouroboros
